<hw>Bul"ly</hw> <pr>(b⟦usdot⟧l"l⟦ycr⟧)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <sn>1.</sn>
<def>Jovial and blustering; dashing.</def> <mark>[Slang]</mark>
